{"aid": "jei4mb99pepnj", "result": {"status": "active", "unique_views": 9, "request_instructor_me": false, "change_log": [{"type": "create", "anon": "no", "when": "2018-03-08T03:33:59Z", "data": "jehyk37j57bbh", "uid": "isu0wqaoff5125"}, {"type": "update", "anon": "no", "when": "2018-03-08T03:35:14Z", "data": "jehylol8w3s1v1", "uid": "isu0wqaoff5125"}, {"to": "jehyk37h8hqbg", "anon": "no", "when": "2018-03-08T03:49:07Z", "type": "followup", "uid": "isu0wqaoff5125"}, {"type": "update", "anon": "no", "when": "2018-03-08T04:45:34Z", "data": "jei1452vip83f", "uid": "ie7xy7fdgfm1sb"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "jehyk37h8hqbg", "bookmarked": 2, "no_answer": 1, "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [{"folders": [], "updated": "2018-03-08T03:49:07Z", "no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "isu0wqaoff5125", "created": "2018-03-08T03:49:07Z", "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "id": "jehz3jbb4w92eg", "anon": "no", "bucket_name": "Today", "config": {}, "bucket_order": 2, "data": null, "children": [], "subject": "<p></p><p>首先&#xff0c;对于每一个任务&#xff08;进程或者线程&#xff09;而言&#xff0c;它有两组寄存器上下文信息。</p>\n<p>一个是该任务自身控制流的上下文&#xff0c;一般是在该任务通过某种方式&#xff08;比如中断或者系统调用&#xff09;主动或被动进入内核时保存的&#xff0c;存于<code>trapframe</code>结构体中&#xff0c;存于该任务的内核栈中&#xff0c;此任务的控制块存放一个指向它的指针。若任务是内核线程&#xff0c;任务的栈与其内核栈是一个&#xff0c;但这不是问题。</p>\n<p>另外一个是该任务进入内核后&#xff0c;对应的内核控制流的上下文&#xff0c;存于<code>context</code>结构体中&#xff0c;嵌在任务的控制块中。</p>\n<p>值得注意的是&#xff0c;为统一起见&#xff0c;内核线程也包含有这两个部分。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>&#xff08;待续&#xff09;</p>"}], "nr": 1143, "bucket_order": 2, "type": "question", "folders": ["2018"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor": 0, "tags": ["2018", "student", "unanswered"], "created": "2018-03-08T03:33:59Z", "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "s_edits": [], "my_favorite": false, "default_anonymity": "no", "t": 1520490221181, "tag_good": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "history": [{"content": "<p>如题。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>感觉这个需要好好讨论一下。</p>", "ano